# 📰 Fake News Detection System (ML + NLP)

This project is a Machine Learning-based Fake News Detection system that classifies news articles as REAL or FAKE using Natural Language Processing (NLP) techniques and a trained classification model.

---

# 🚀 Project Overview

The goal of this project is to detect misleading or false news articles using text classification techniques.

---

# 🧠 Features

- Text preprocessing
- TF-IDF vectorization
- Logistic Regression model
- Gradio web interface for real-time prediction
- User-friendly input system

---

# 📊 Input

- News article text

---

# 🎯 Output

- REAL NEWS 🟢
- FAKE NEWS 🔴

---

# 🛠️ Tech Stack

- Python
- Pandas
- Scikit-learn
- NLP (TF-IDF)
- Gradio

---

# 🚀 How to Run

```bash
pip install gradio scikit-learn pandas numpy
python fake_news.py
